				<p><span class="p_starter">Who are we? </span>We are: 1 English teacher, 1 computer scientist, 1 children's illustrator, + several brilliant academics who advise us. We're based in London, UK. Read more about the team {{#link-to 'about' class="underline"}}here.{{/link-to}}</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>


